<subSubSection pageId="18" pageNumber="169" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="18.[151,1436,1843,2014]" pageId="18" pageNumber="169">
Ståhls 
<emphasis box="[226,275,1843,1869]" italics="true" pageId="18" pageNumber="169">et al</emphasis>
. (2008) found three different clades in the COI sequences of specimens of the 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Fallen" baseAuthorityYear="1817" box="[1150,1272,1843,1870]" class="Insecta" family="Syrphidae" genus="Cheilosia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="18" pageNumber="169" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="vernalis">
<emphasis box="[1150,1272,1843,1870]" italics="true" pageId="18" pageNumber="169">C. vernalis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
complex from various parts of Europe. However, these clades mismatched with morphological characters. While it is possible that different species are involved, the available identification keys do not allow separating different species. All records of specimens identified as 
<taxonomicName authority="Becker" authorityName="Becker" box="[457,736,1951,1978]" class="Insecta" family="Syrphidae" genus="Cheilosia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="18" pageNumber="169" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="rotundiventris">
<emphasis box="[457,649,1951,1978]" italics="true" pageId="18" pageNumber="169">C. rotundiventris</emphasis>
Becker
</taxonomicName>
or 
<taxonomicName authority="Becker" authorityName="Becker" box="[777,1003,1951,1978]" class="Insecta" family="Syrphidae" genus="Cheilosia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="18" pageNumber="169" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="ruficollis">
<emphasis box="[777,913,1951,1978]" italics="true" pageId="18" pageNumber="169">C. ruficollis</emphasis>
Becker
</taxonomicName>
, both syonymised with 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Fallen" baseAuthorityYear="1817" box="[1275,1399,1951,1978]" class="Insecta" family="Syrphidae" genus="Cheilosia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="18" pageNumber="169" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="vernalis">
<emphasis box="[1275,1399,1951,1978]" italics="true" pageId="18" pageNumber="169">C. vernalis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
by Ståhls 
<emphasis box="[227,276,1987,2013]" italics="true" pageId="18" pageNumber="169">et al</emphasis>
. (2008), have been lumped with 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Fallen" baseAuthorityYear="1817" box="[646,768,1987,2014]" class="Insecta" family="Syrphidae" genus="Cheilosia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="18" pageNumber="169" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="vernalis">
<emphasis box="[646,768,1987,2014]" italics="true" pageId="18" pageNumber="169">C. vernalis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
